			    <h3> The problem </h3>
			    <p>Simulating airflow through the larynx</p>
			    <img width="35%" src="assets/domain_larynx2.png">
			    <img src="assets/larynx.jpg">
								
			  </section>
			  <section>
			    <p>... a complicated geometry in a complicated system</p>

			    <img width="45%" src="assets/respiratory.png"><br>
			  </section>

			  <section>
			    <p>Why?</p>
			    <small>Understand exercise-induced laryngeal obstruction</small>
			    <video controls loop>
			      <source src="assets/video/eilo.m4v"  type="video/mp4"><br>
			    </video>
			    <br><br>
			    <small>Changes in epiglottic fold geometry leading to breathing problems</small>
			    <small>EILO is often misdiagnosed as asthma</small>
			  </section>
			  </section>

			  <section>
			    <h3>The team</h3>
