			  <section>
			    <p>Why COMSOL?</p><br>
			    <ul>
			      <li>Widely used in computer-aided engineering </li><br>
			      <li>Good support for relevant physics: fluid mechanics and structural or solid mechanics </li><br>
			      <li>Rapid prototyping. Short iterations.</li><br>
			      <li>Flexible: custom differential and algebraic equations </li><br>
			      <li>Compatible with other tools (especially MATLAB)</li>
			    </ul>
			  </section>
			  </section>
			  -->
