			    <section>
			      <h3>Part 1, Step 1:<br></h3> a more realistic geometry
			    </section>

			  </section>

			    <section>
			      Meet Mr. Horse <br>
			      <img src="assets/horse.jpg">
			    </section>
			    <section>
			      <p>A former elite thoroughbred racehorse that won numerous high profile races.</p> <p>Died after an operation. Larynx excised and imaged.</p>
			      <img width="55%" src="assets/horse_ct.gif">
			    </section>


			    <section>
			      Constructing a 3D model from the CT data<br>
			      <div class="fragment">
			      <p>Segmentation: Locating and separating structures of interest in an image.</p>
			      <div class="fragment">			      
			      <p> Can use e.g. <a href="itksnap.org">ITK-SNAP</a> to do semiautomatic segmentation using active contours.</p>
			      <video width="320" height="240" controls>
				<source src="assets/itk-movie.mp4" type="video/mp4">
				  Your browser does not support the video tag.
			      </video>
			      <div class="fragment">
			      <br>
			      <small>Many open questions related to segmentation will be investigated</small>
			      </div>
			      </div>
			      </div>
			    </section>
			    

