			  <section>
			    <section>
			      <h3>The physics</h3>
			      <div class="fragment">
			      <p>Fluid flow: Navier-Stokes. Turbulent flow. </p>
			      <p>Structural mechanics: pressure and viscous forces
			      <p>Fluid-structure interaction (FSI): deformable and moving structures interacting with internal fluid flow <br><div class="fragment"> <div style="text-align: center"><a href="http://idac.co.uk/images/products/multiphysics/ANSYS_Multiphysics_Fluid_Structure_Interaction_of_a_Three-Lobe_Valve_Image.jpg"><img width="200px"  src="http://idac.co.uk/images/products/multiphysics/ANSYS_Multiphysics_Fluid_Structure_Interaction_of_a_Three-Lobe_Valve_Image.jpg"></a>
				    <button onclick="changeImage(2);"> &nbsp; &nbsp; <img width="450px" id="image2" src="assets/blood1.png"> </button></div></p>
			      </div>
			      </div>
			    </section>
			  </section>

