			  <section>
			    <section>
			      <h3>The mesh</h3>
			      <div class="fragment">
			      <span class="c_blue"><em>"Grid design is an art"</em>
			      </span>
			      
			    <div class="fragment">
			    <p>Complicated geometry: must use coarse mesh on parts of domain to lower computation time</p>
			    <p class="fragment">Refined near rapidly moving vocal folds </p>
			    <p class="fragment">Adapt mesh to solution: use flow properties to recalculate optimal node locations</p> 
			    <p class="fragment">Conforming mesh: fluid-structure interaction</p>
			    <p class="fragment">Study mesh sensitivity</p>
			    </div>
			      </div>
			    </section>
