			  <section>
			    <section>
			      <h3>The analysis</h3>
			      <div class="fragment">
			      <ul>
				<li>Validate: compare aerodynamical results with lab measurements. 3D printed version tested in wind tunnel</li><br>
			      <li class="fragment">Predict: predict the effect of abnormal anatomy or function (e.g. exercise-induced laryngeal obstruction)</li><br>
			      <li class="fragment">Modify: predict the effect of surgery and medication</li><br>
			      </ul>
			      </div>
			    </section>
			  </section>

